## Compression/extraction.

### 7z
alias 7zcat="7z e -bd -so"

### Rar

alias rarcat="unrar p"

### Zip

alias zipcat="unzip -p"

### ZStandard (zstd).

alias tarzs-rm="tar -cv --remove-files --zstd -f"
